CC  This property describes the biosynthesis of bacillithiol, a thiol
CC  analog of glutathione and mycothiol. Bacillithiol is a 398-Da
CC  alpha-anomeric glycoside of L-cysteinyl-D-glucosamine with L-malic acid.
